| Metric                | Global Python         | Virtual Environment |
| --------------------- | --------------------- | ------------------- |
| Dependency conflicts  | 87% projects affected | 0%                  |
| Deployment failures   | 23% version mismatch  | <1%                 |
| Team onboarding time  | 2-4 hours             | 15 minutes          |
